OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will often be wet today in
OL,6,Fsouthern areas with rain at times.
OL,7,FFurther north it looks mostly dry,
OL,8,Falbeit largely cloudy. Very mild with
OL,9,Flight winds, though feeling cooler in
OL,10,Fany rain.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FRather damp in the south this
OL,13,Fevening but turning generally dry
OL,14,Fovernight with the odd remaining
OL,15,Fshower. A colder night with the
OL,16,Fpossibility of the odd frost and fog
OL,17,Fpatch.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
