OL,2,W+.-'"-$/*%*%*%/"-$/*%Q,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA few showers through the
OL,6,Fmorning, but for most it will be a dry
OL,7,Fday with cloud alternating with
OL,8,Foccasional sunny intervals. Somewhat
OL,9,Fless mild but winds generally light.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWetter
OL,12,Fand windier on Sunday with occasional
OL,13,Fdrizzly rain, this most frequent over
OL,14,Fthe hills. Generally drier on Monday
OL,15,Fbut showery rain still possible.
OL,16,FPerhaps brighter on Tuesday. Staying
OL,17,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
